NG0400:1100: spyad par bya ba nyams gyur na /
NG0400:1101: khams gsum sems can srog gcad la //

NG0400:1110: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa @#//

NG0400:1141: dam tshig nyams pa phog ste de ma gsos pas
